==Welsh==

===Pronunciation===
: ā-stĕTH'vŏd / eye-stĕTH'vŏd

===Etymology===
:From Welsh eistedd (sitting) and bod (to be)

===Proper noun===
'''Eisteddfod'''

# An [[annual]] [[festival]] in which [[Welsh]] [[poet]]s, [[dancer]]s and [[musician]]s [[compete]] for [[recognition]].

'''Eisteddfod motto'''

:"Byd gwyn fydd byd a gano,
:Gwaraidd fydd ei gerddi fo"

:''"Blessed is a world that sings,
:Gentle are its songs"''